Cell[TextData[{
 "1. A newspaper asks two of its staff to review the coffee quality at \
different trendy caf\[EAcute]s. The coffee can be rated on a scale from 1 \
(miserable) to 10 (excellent). The results of the two coffee enthusiasts X \
and Y are as follows:\n",
