Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
2. We are interested in the pizza delivery data previously discussed.
(a) Read in the data and create two new binary variables which describe \
whether a pizza was hot (>65 \[EmptySmallCircle]C) and the delivery time was \
short (<30 min). Create a contingency table for the two new variables.
(b) Calculate and interpret the odds ratio for the contingency table from \
(a).
(c) Use Cramer\[CloseCurlyQuote]s V and a stacked bar chart to explore the \
association between the categorical time and temperature variables.
(d) Draw a scatter plot for the continuous time and temperature variables. \
Determine
both the Bravais\[Dash]Pearson and Spearman correlation coefficients.
(e) Use methods of your choice to explore the relationship between \
temperature
and driver, operator, number of ordered pizzas and bill. Is it clear which of \
the
variables influence the pizza temperature?\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9471200295656347`*^9, 3.9471200303704433`*^9}, {
  3.947120063241949*^9, 3.94712011070362*^9}, {3.979295250352709*^9, 
  3.979295255465317*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7ebc109c-867f-498b-96af-\
8e02dd71cc25"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", "a", "*)"}], "\n", "\n", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"pdt", " ", "=", " ", 
     RowBox[{
     "Import", 
      "[", "\"\<D:\\\\University_of_Aberdeen\\\\Semester_2\\\\PX5510_\
Statistics_and_Time_Series_Analysis\\\\Lecture \
Practicals\\\\pizza_delivery.csv\>\"", "]"}]}], ";"}], "\n", 
   RowBox[{"shortcold", " ", "=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"Length", "[", 
     RowBox[{"Select", "[", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"pdt", "[", 
        RowBox[{"[", 
         RowBox[{"2", ";;"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"#", "[", 
           RowBox[{"[", "3", "]"}], "]"}], "<", "30"}], "&&", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"#", "[", 
           RowBox[{"[", "7", "]"}], "]"}], "<=", "65"}]}], "&"}]}], "]"}], 
     "]"}]}], "\n", 
   RowBox[{"longcold", " ", "=", "  ", 
    RowBox[{"Length", "[", 
     RowBox[{"Select", "[", 
      RowBox[{
